data.description: Priced to sell. Great price located in Bayshore Gardens. 3 bedroom/2 full bath/plus bonus room located in highly sought after Bayshore Gardens. Features include tile throughout, new metal roof installed in 2013, newer windows, master walk in shower, laundry room with sink, open room concept with kitchen, dining room and living room all open. Located just minutes from the Sarasota Bradenton airport with easy access to downtown Sarasota or downtown Bradenton. Bayshore Garden Parks & Recreation providing a Jr. Olympic-size swimming pool, playground, picnic pavilions and BBQ grills throughout the park, recreation hall with kitchen, a ball field, basketball courts, fishing pier and marina complete with community boat ramp. Just 5 miles from the Gulf Beaches of Anna Maria Island.
